title: 2019 Week 7 Preview
itunes:title: 2019 Week 7 Preview
description:
A room full of heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview each upcoming game of the Week 7 NFL match ups while still fighting the jet-lag! Can the Jets upset the Patriots? Marc and Wess go in on a lock together! Could the Bills be a top seed in the AFC? Go listen now!
